imdb.plot outline: A killer, Analia is paid to kill a businesswoman, Mariana Montiel. After the car they were in gets off the road and burns to flames, two doctors find the body of Mariana and a photo of the face of Analia. They fix Analia's face into Mariana's body. That's where the confusion will begin.
imdb.title: El Rostro de Analía
plot: A killer, Analia is paid to kill a businesswoman, Mariana Montiel. After the car they were in gets off the road and burns to flames, two doctors find the body of Mariana and a photo of the face of Analia. They fix Analia's face into Mariana's body. That's where the confusion will begin.
